			"y":-5160,
			"width":600,
			"height":340
		},
		{
			"id":"d31b4ef5baf15970",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"creatures should have a mass statistic. this would be useful for various things, namely checking anthurium poison levels\n\nalso i kinda want to make a godot plugin that lets me see all the components i've written easy access perhaps with a description. this should probably be its own window kinda like adding a node to a scene but the window should be like a grid with categories. is this possible? not sure",
