			"x":-19230,
			"y":-6796,
			"width":260,
			"height":170
		},
		{
			"id":"c020edbb4570e7b5",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# The game begins",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-19210,
			"y":-7126,
			"width":260,
			"height":170
		},
		{
			"id":"a64f97ba63f65eba",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# Game mechanics\n\n### Creatures\nCreatures have unique properties and behavior patterns that influence the state of the arena.\n\n**Analysis**: Creatures are the backbone of this game, making the board feel alive with a fantastical ecosystem.\n\n### Anthurium\nThe plantlike god entity acting as the main source of chaos in the arena.\n\n### Abilities\nNot only do creatures themselves have unique properties and behaviors, but they also possess unique abilities. Ability shards can be dropped from creatures and absorbed by any other entity.\n\n\n### Aura\nNot yet implemented, but this could act as a metric for how \"successful\" a round is. Basically points from arcade games?\n\n### Ichor\nActs as a centralized resource pool for creatures. Using some abilities drains it. It also drains slowly over time. Eating food fills it. When it's empty, the creature will start slowly losing health.\n\n### Terrain\nTerrain can be created or destroyed during the game, changing up the game board dynamically.\n\n\n### Vision\nThe player can only see entities in the room they are currently in. Any entities or terrain outside the walls are not visible.\n\n**Analysis**: This gives the game the illusion of depth; because the game board is only 64x64, we can stuff more features into the map and have the player discover them as the game progresses. This gives the player an excited and curious feeling, wondering what else could be beyond the walls.\n\n**Possible Issues**: The player must have some indication on where or how to reach different rooms/caves of the game board, otherwise this mechanic could get frustrating. ",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-19890,
			"y":-7166,
			"width":500,
			"height":1360
		},
		{"id":"d0ce50e1682adec4","type":"file","file":"assets/b9a8afc838c0c26dcd4b72884d38ac30.jpg","x":-10440,"y":-17709,"width":400,"height":240},
		{"id":"6529d1de046bd420","type":"file","file":"assets/03aca7785e04b8e64b53a93098a54ea6.gif","x":-10440,"y":-18169,"width":500,"height":460},
		{"id":"4a04a95aba69295d","type":"file","file":"assets/a8a7dcec34fd2b1cbe978486706f5a9a.gif","x":-10440,"y":-18576,"width":844,"height":407},
		{"id":"7ed5d186a3c410a0","type":"file","file":"assets/original_025070e5d893cecc740d90dfec23cf93.gif","x":-9595,"y":-18169,"width":564,"height":460},
