		{
			"id":"6353630d295c213d",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# todo 6/11/2026:\n- [x] portal object to show where an entity is spawning\n- [ ] pickupable tiles (graphical data is transferred)\n- [x] rework anthurium movement and look, place down root tiles\n- [ ] bomb guy that blows up on contact with any entity\n- [ ] fix `ecube_gamma` not blowing everything up (weird bug)\n- [x] tool to help with making sounds\n- [x] tool to help with particle creation\n- [ ] make particle system work for screen space as well as world space\n- [x] system to link up tilemap coordinates to cell properties\n- [x] revisit how the tilemap implementation works, maybe add a dictionary that describes terrain types (look into CellData) (maybe resources that define every themed terrain look/type/property)\n>  There's two different types of tile sources!\n>  TILING: every tile is made of the same material and are visually connected to each other to form a surface\n>  NON-TILING: every tile is a representation of a different object\n- [x] figure out a good way to set up aura and ichor\n- [ ] a death screen / restart run interface\n- [ ] text formatting codes\n- [ ] configure ability descriptions\n- [ ] make ability icons bounce when they are pressed\n- [x] add a CRT filter\n- [ ] add functionality to reorganize and move around HUD elements\n- [ ] make an EntityEffect that casts an ability!\n- [ ] refine lerping camera and make it have a bit of a deadzone tracking the player\n- [ ] make BloomEvents\n- [ ] program in the anthurium brain\n- [ ] add anthurium BloomEvent support\n- [ ] add the bones of the main menu!\n- [x] EntityEffect that spawns another entity\n\n# todo 06/21/2026\n- [ ] z-axis standalone component\n- [x] EntityEffect that shakes the screen\n- [ ] make it so that camera follows random entity when dead\n- [ ] ichor / food / starvation",
