		{
			"id":"6de0f7f3cb494cfd",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# Bloom ideas\n- the anthurium begins drawing ichor from nearby creatures\n- jumpy bug swarp with mother bug appearance, kill her to stop the swarm (when mother is killed, all bugs instantly die dropping nutritious meat)\n- a sinkhole opens up with a dragon worm inside\n- the plant goes into overdrive, spreading and eating all matter aggressively\n- interdimensional alien beings invade\n- nine wizards appear and start transforming the dungeon\n- the anthurium is split into multiple fragments spread out all across the board\n- everything lights on fire\n- everything turns into a swamp\n- the undead come back to life\n- the dungeon's zones are picked up and moved around\n- magic, colorful, unstable living crystals grow forth from the anthurium\n- summon a powerful creature",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-13060,
			"y":-1780,
			"width":660,
			"height":1160
		},
		{
			"id":"5d6184c785dacbc8",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# This is the final iteration of the Anthurium.\nlets all say our congratulations because it's been a long and wild ride.",
