		{
			"id":"3d35e07a8906417f",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"MASS: an entity parameter\n\ntiny: 0-5\nmedium: 5-25\nlarge: 25-100\nhulking: >100\n\nused for entity behavior calculations. predatory creatures tend to go for PASSIVE creatures that are less massive than itself unless it is starving or has help.",
